<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>FightClub</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/navbar.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/signup.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <main class="container">
      <div class="hero">
        <h1>Welcome to FightClub</h1>
        <p class="tagline">
          The first rule of FightClub: You do not talk about FightClub.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <div class="card">
          <h2>About Us</h2>
          <p>
            We are a community of individuals who have lost everything. We are
            the middle children of history, raised by television to believe that
            someday we'll be millionaires and movie stars and rock stars, but we
            won't.
          </p>
          <div class="quotes">
            <p class="quote">
              "You are not your job, you're not how much money you have in the
              bank. You are not the car you drive. You're not the contents of
              your wallet."
            </p>
            <p class="quote">
              "It's only after we've lost everything that we're free to do
              anything."
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <% if(locals.user && !locals.user.is_member) {%>
        <div class="card">
          <h2>Become a Member</h2>
          <p>
            Become a member of our private club and discover what you're truly
            capable of.
          </p>
          <a href="/member" class="signup-button">Become Member</a>
        </div>
        <%} else if(locals.user && locals.user.is_member) {%>
        <div class="card">
          <h2>Welcome Back, Member!</h2>
          <p>
            Welcome back to the club! We hope you're ready to embrace the chaos
            and discover your true self.
          </p>
        </div>
        <%} else {%>

        <div class="card">
          <h2>Join Us</h2>
          <p>
            It's only after we've lost everything that we're free to do
            anything. Join our exclusive club and discover what you're truly
            capable of.
          </p>
          <a href="/signup" class="signup-button">Sign Up</a>
        </div>
        <%}%>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
